unittitle_ssm: Dutch Reformed churches of Brooklyn collection
abstract_ssm: The Dutch Reformed churches of Brooklyn collection spans the period 1856 to 1971 and documents the activities of various Reformed churches in Brooklyn. Materials include clippings, yearbooks, rule books, bulletins, programs, reports, and histories.
